<header class="music-heading">
  <div class="intro-body">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
          <h2>My Music</h2>
          <p class="intro-text">
            Music has always been a large part of my life. Much like programming, music is a craft that you endlessly practise, improve and refine. There is always something new to master and
            it is always fun. From an early age, I found practising the piano was a way to unwind and escape for while.
          </p>
          <p class="intro-text">
            Scroll down for a peek at some of my music projects to date.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="#my-music-projects" class="arrow js-scroll-trigger">
        <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-down animated fa-4x"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
        <h2 id="my-music-projects">My Projects</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="thumbnail">
          <!-- 16:9 aspect ratio -->
          <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
            <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fIoKG9-ZnJw" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>Bach's Prelude in C</h3>
            <p>One of Bach's well known and easily accessible preludes has made this piece a must learn for piano students. In addition to this, this piece is a popular choice for wedding ceremonies.</p>
            <p>Using <%= link_to 'Ableton', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ableton_Live', target: '_blank' %>, <%= link_to 'OBS', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_Broadcaster_Software', target: '_blank' %> and <%= link_to 'Synthesia', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Synthesia', target: '_blank' %> I recorded my performance and put together a visual tutorial as to how it is played so the viewer can learn to play it for themselves. Have a little watch yourself.</p>
            <p>To view more of my Synthesia videos on YouTube, click on the button below</p>
            <%= link_to 'View on YouTube', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fIoKG9-ZnJw&list=UUJCLykUyNiUHtK-2T6wjkow', target: '_blank', class: 'btn btn-default' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">

    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="card col-lg-3">
        <%= image_tag 'samurai_and_ninja.jpg', alt: 'card image', class: 'card-img-top' %>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Ninja vs. Samurai</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            An object orientated, RPG console application, used as an exercise to become more fluent with many OOP Concepts. It is tested using MiniTest and Test::Unit
          </p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">Written in <span class="ruby-color">Ruby</span></li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <%= link_to 'View on GitHub', 'https://github.com/yamadaj2/object_orientated_game', target: '_blank', class: 'btn btn-default' %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card col-lg-3">
        <%= image_tag 'pencil.jpg', alt: 'card image', class: 'card-img-top' %>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Alpha Blog</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            This is a demo app demonstrating CRUD functionality.
            The app has sign up feature and allows authorised users to create, read and update posts and comments.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">Written with <span class="ruby-color">Ruby on Rails</span></li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <%= link_to 'View on GitHub', 'https://github.com/yamadaj2/alpha-blog', target: '_blank', class: 'btn btn-default' %>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card col-lg-3">
        <%= image_tag 'site-header.png', alt: 'card image', class: 'card-img-top' %>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">My Personal Site</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            This site you are currently viewing is a <span class="ruby-color">Ruby on Rails</span> application.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <%= link_to 'View on GitHub', 'https://github.com/yamadaj2/alpha-blog', target: '_blank', class: 'btn btn-default' %>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

